hopobject.body: Have you seen any good films recently? costco pharmacy wilsonville Dempsey has already proven without any doubt that he's a high-caliber Premiership player, scoring 29 goals in his final two seasons at Fulham while mostly playing as an outside midfielder. There is absolutely no reason for him to go to a lesser side such as Sunderland or Swansea or West Ham and do what he's already done, which is the crux of this entire decision, in my opinion.
